race.comment: ROTAGILLA (3) progressive gelding who brings the right figures to take this out, second-up. Drifted back early when resuming before striking trouble in the straight when an unlucky fourth over 1400m at Warwick Farm. Expected to overcome the sticky gate and prove hard to hold out. STRAWBERRY IMPACT (4) fourth-up for this and a win looks imminent. Surged late from back in the field when fourth to Modella over 1400m at Rosehill. No surprise to see him closer to the speed with the 52.5kg. Leading prospect. CHICAMA (5) got off the mark at start five defeating a handy field over 1400m at Warwick Farm with the 59kg. Drops on the limit and stays in the mix. PLACID PEARL (8) chipped away late on resumption and will keep improving as she gets out in trip.
